  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿，士兵，我又给你找了些活儿，感兴趣吗？太好了！\n我刚搞到一批M203下挂榴弹发射器，但还没找人测试过，所以得请你帮个忙。你能用这榴弹发射器或者装上了它的武器干掉几个目标吗？那再好不过了，等你的消息。",
    "en": "Well hello soldier, I got something for you again, you interested? Great!\nI just got access to M203 underbarrel grenade launchers, but I didn't have anyone to test them out, so I need your help here. Are you able to take out some targets with the grenadelauncher or weapons that have it attached? That would be great, I'll hear from you later."
  },
